WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
narrator: mint a single-use preauth key for one user.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.500
narrator: the key is one-shot — usable by exactly one tailscale up.

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:17.000
narrator: a reusable key with a 24-hour TTL suits fleet rollouts.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:22.000
narrator: the same surface is exposed over HTTP for daemon callers.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:27.700
narrator: POST /admin/preauth, Bearer-gated, JSON body — identical shape.
